headline.print_headline: A W.N.B.A. Star Is Ready For Her Farewell Tour
headline.main: Tamika Catchings Is Ready for Her Farewell Tour

snippet: Catchings, an Indiana Fever player who has become an ambassador for women’s basketball, will close out a career that included 10 All-Star appearances and a W.N.B.A. title.
lead_paragraph: Catchings, an Indiana Fever player who has become an ambassador for women’s basketball, will close out a career that included 10 All-Star appearances and a W.N.B.A. title.
